{
  "name": "RPlog_Playing_for_Time",
  "title": "Playing for Time",
  "summary": "Aboard the shuttle Darklighter, the archaeologist Paul Nighman waits anxiously for the street-smart young woman Shenner to return from carrying a message to Luke Skywalker. She reports that Luke believes the dangerous V'ez-tcha group, led by Grathix, may be holding General Han Solo, and wants to meet them before Paul approaches Grathix about recovering certain artifacts. Paul, bound for hazardous work on Mandalore, tries to send Shenner to safety with Luke, but she stubbornly insists on staying at his side, and he relents, taking her on as his \"assistant.\" To pass the time and prepare her, Paul gives Shenner an extended lesson in field first aid and survival, covering shock, pulse points, wound care, and the rules of staying calm in an emergency. The interlude ends tenderly as Paul plays his guitar and Shenner accompanies him on her ocarina before drifting off to sleep, the bond between them quietly deepening.",
